915
00:39:33.690 --> 00:39:36.650
<font color="#ffffff">* Applaus *</font>

916
00:39:41.120 --> 00:39:43.940
<font color="#00ffff">Guten Abend, Louis Perron.</font>

917
00:39:44.610 --> 00:39:47.260
<font color="#00ffff">Kann man mit Geld</font>
